Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為 提到椎名真白…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}天才畫家…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你才是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}入浴場景好像不夠撩情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.39,0:00:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛤？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}綾乃她是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 是在說漫畫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別…別對著臉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打濕的臉相當耐人尋味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.27,0:00:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在的我就那麼嫵媚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.69,0:00:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大致上了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼 了解什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等 你要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回房間 繼續畫原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這蓮蓬頭就這麼放著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:00:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}新人獎的截稿日期快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就不能從正面回答一下我的問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.67,0:01:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夠了 回房間去加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}油？油炸豆腐？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要加油的是誰啊
