Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:54.66,Note,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs60\c&H6A59C0&\shad0\pos(474,474)}黑的就是你啊（笑）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比剛才更惡劣了！
